ild state is ","type":"text"},{"code":"nil","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":"’d out. This gives the parent feature an opportunity to","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"inspect the child state one last time before the state is cleared.","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"When a ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/PresentationAction\/presented(_:)","type":"reference"},{"text":" action is sent it runs the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"child first, and then the parent. If the order was reversed, then it would be possible","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"for the parent feature to ","type":"text"},{"code":"nil","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" out the child state, in which case the child feature","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"would not be able to react to that action. That can cause subtle bugs.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"It automatically cancels all child effects when it detects the child’s state is ","type":"text"},{"code":"nil","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":"’d","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"out.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Automatically ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"nil"},{"text":"s out child state when an action is sent for alerts and confirmation","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"dialogs.","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"It gives the child feature access to the "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/DismissEffect"},{"type":"text","text":" dependency, which allows the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"child feature to dismiss itself without communicating with t